metadata.name: Demons Also Cry #1/50
metadata.description:
All living beings experience emotions. And that's okay. It's not shameful. Do not be ashamed to cry if you feel bad, if you are sad, if you are just tired or feel exhausted.

You smile but black tears flow from your eyes. What did they do to you? Did you deserve it?

Cry dear, and then go into battle with renewed vigor!
